{"about_the_game":"\u201cCaseCrack 2\u201d .the sequel story of \u201cCaseCracker\u201d, is also a text-based detective puzzle game.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294450/extras/2.png?t=1728987104\" /><br>As the invited tester, you need to check all the existing clues and information in each case , search for key words and continuously find out more clues.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294450/extras/\u641c\u7d22.gif?t=1728987104\" /><br><br>While sorting out the fragmented information, you need to reason out and finish tasks such as \u201cmonitor surveillance\u201d, \u201csearch warrant\u201d, \u201csystem access\u201d and \u201cdecryption\u201d.  <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294450/extras/\u7279\u6b8a\u64cd\u4f5c.gif?t=1728987104\" /><br><br>After collecting all the information , you need to reason out the treads and plots of the whole case, and answer the question of the system to solve the case, after the solution, you can review the records from the \u201cCriminal statement\u201d. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294450/extras/\u53d1\u9001\u62a5\u544a.gif?t=1728987104\" /><br><br>You will have a more immersive experience of cracking a criminal case like a policeman   under the system rules with the realistic narrative story . <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294450/extras/3.png?t=1728987104\" /><br><br>You will experience a step-by-step progress of cracking the case with the complex and intricate plot and story where there lie some cross-over relationship among different characters and cases.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294450/extras/\u4eba\u7269\u67e5\u770b.gif?t=1728987104\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294450/extras/1.png?t=1728987104\" /><br><br>Beside the mainline, there are also some other bizarre branch and invisible line needed to be dig out. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294450/extras/\u97f3\u9891gif.gif?t=1728987104\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294450/extras/4.png?t=1728987104\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Players need to find out the clues all by themselves, since there is no alternatives provided. </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>All the cases happen in one world, independently yet related with each other</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The invisible clue line can be explored beyond the game story, </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Please take it seriously for each choice you make in the one-round word game!</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"S.O.S.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2294450/c33d91abdfff4a276e7df0de8ca8c35e5635c202.jpg"},{"name":"Data Statistics","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2294450/9603d044fe84e00d6849d546f46d6c5a116d464a.jpg"},{"name":"Barren Hills","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2294450/3eaff3aef95b4e01631ecd0ddd4cbc24cc8d89aa.jpg"},{"name":"Beautiful Prague","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2294450/b226406b3098967ed976460aef09347b2cfd90f6.jpg"},{"name":"Beautiful San Francisco","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2294450/5f0c3f0af25a1adc86653a7e53670d1dc6e72736.jpg"},{"name":"Beautiful Omaha","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2294450/42eff7c06fdf6c594c7